        &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;item&#34; title=&#34;Linn&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://yanglinzhuo.github.io/&#34; class=&#34;image&#34; data-background-image=&#34;https://yanglinzhuo.github.io/images/my_small_avatar.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
